To install mpi4py with Anaconda:
    `conda install mpi4py`

Python commands can be executed in parallel on Blue Waters with
    `aprun (options) python (filename).py`

On your own laptop, replace `aprun` with either `mpirun` or `mpiexec` (whichever works)

Examples copied with permission from Dr. Brian W O'Shea at Michigan State Univ
